wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"What better place\", \"from\": 8391, \"to\": 8409}, {\"ngram\": \"this magic\", \"from\": 8431, \"to\": 8441}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 8445, \"to\": 8462}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole world\", \"from\": 8468, \"to\": 8483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 president Tony Estanguet, a three-time Olympic gold medallist in canoe slalom, is speaking now.\", \"from\": 8487, \"to\": 8593, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8489, \"end\": 8499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1372984376837397e-36, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 8510, \"end\": 8524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a three-time Olympic gold medallist\", \"from\": 8524, \"to\": 8559}, {\"ngram\": \"canoe slalom\", \"from\": 8563, \"to\": 8575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"France is often said to be the country of love,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 8595, \"to\": 8653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8598, \"end\": 8604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999999690772, \"rank\": 3.1072111363605914e-11, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 8623, \"to\": 8634}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 8638, \"to\": 8642}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"One thing I know is that here, when we love, we truly love.\", \"from\": 8654, \"to\": 8714, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One thing\", \"from\": 8655, \"to\": 8664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And between France and the Games, there has been a big love story\\\".\", \"from\": 8715, \"to\": 8782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8729, \"end\": 8735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999999690772, \"rank\": 3.1072111363605914e-11, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 8738, \"to\": 8747}, {\"ngram\": \"a big love story\", \"from\": 8764, \"to\": 8780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Estanguet said carrying on the legacy \\\"born nearly 130 years ago\\\" was \\\"a huge responsibility, so we have put our whole hearts into it.\", \"from\": 8784, \"to\": 8921, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mr Estanguet\", \"from\": 8784, \"to\": 8796}, {\"ngram\": \"the legacy\", \"from\": 8814, \"to\": 8824}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge responsibility\", \"from\": 8858, \"to\": 8879}, {\"ngram\": \"our whole hearts\", \"from\": 8896, \"to\": 8912}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To love the Games is to court the Games for 100 years, for the chance to bring them back to Paris.\", \"from\": 8922, \"to\": 9020, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9016, \"end\": 9021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.794026023152485e-32, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 8930, \"to\": 8939}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 8952, \"to\": 8961}, {\"ngram\": \"100 years\", \"from\": 8966, \"to\": 8975}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 8981, \"to\": 8991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you are madly in love with the Games, you feel like you can do anything.\", \"from\": 9022, \"to\": 9100, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 9045, \"to\": 9049}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 9055, \"to\": 9064}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 9091, \"to\": 9099}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have been bold, doing things that have never been done before, like having this opening ceremony in the city for the first time in the history of the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 9101, \"to\": 9268, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 9126, \"to\": 9132}, {\"ngram\": \"this opening ceremony\", \"from\": 9179, \"to\": 9200}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 9204, \"to\": 9212}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 9217, \"to\": 9231}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 9235, \"to\": 9246}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 9250, \"to\": 9267}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Like every host country our ambition has been to help the Games grow stronger.\\\"\", \"from\": 9270, \"to\": 9350, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every host country\", \"from\": 9276, \"to\": 9294}, {\"ngram\": \"our ambition\", \"from\": 9295, \"to\": 9307}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 9325, \"to\": 9334}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Addressing the thousands of athletes in attendance, he said: \\\"What a sight it is to see you all parading together.\", \"from\": 9352, \"to\": 9466, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the thousands\", \"from\": 9363, \"to\": 9376}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 9380, \"to\": 9388}, {\"ngram\": \"attendance\", \"from\": 9392, \"to\": 9402}, {\"ngram\": \"What a sight\", \"from\": 9414, \"to\": 9426}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What a rare and precious moment you have given us.\", \"from\": 9467, \"to\": 9517, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"What a rare and precious moment\", \"from\": 9467, \"to\": 9498}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 9514, \"to\": 9516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And even though the Games cannot solve every problem, even though discrimination and conflicts are not about to disappear, tonight you have reminded us how beautiful humanity is when we come together.\", \"from\": 9518, \"to\": 9718, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 9534, \"to\": 9543}, {\"ngram\": \"every problem\", \"from\": 9557, \"to\": 9570}, {\"ngram\": \"discrimination\", \"from\": 9584, \"to\": 9598}, {\"ngram\": \"conflicts\", \"from\": 9603, \"to\": 9612}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 9667, \"to\": 9669}, {\"ngram\": \"how beautiful humanity\", \"from\": 9670, \"to\": 9692}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And when you return to the Olympic Village, you will be sending a message of hope to the whole world, that there is a place where people of every nationality, every culture and every religion can live together.\", \"from\": 9720, \"to\": 9931, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9750, \"end\": 9765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.431399504317824e-29, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 9785, \"to\": 9794}, {\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 9798, \"to\": 9802}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole world\", \"from\": 9806, \"to\": 9821}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 9837, \"to\": 9844}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 9851, \"to\": 9857}, {\"ngram\": \"every nationality\", \"from\": 9861, \"to\": 9878}, {\"ngram\": \"every culture\", \"from\": 9880, \"to\": 9893}, {\"ngram\": \"every religion\", \"from\": 9898, \"to\": 9912}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You will be reminding us of what's possible.\", \"from\": 9932, \"to\": 9976, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 9954, \"to\": 9956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For the next 16 days, you will be the best version of humanity.\", \"from\": 9978, \"to\": 10042, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the next 16 days\", \"from\": 9983, \"to\": 9999}, {\"ngram\": \"the best version\", \"from\": 10013, \"to\": 10029}, {\"ngram\": \"humanity\", \"from\": 10033, \"to\": 10041}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You will remind us that the emotions of sport form a universal language that we all share.\", \"from\": 10043, \"to\": 10133, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 10059, \"to\": 10061}, {\"ngram\": \"the emotions\", \"from\": 10067, \"to\": 10079}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 10083, \"to\": 10088}, {\"ngram\": \"a universal language\", \"from\": 10094, \"to\": 10114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Until the 11th of August, we will be by your side.\", \"from\": 10134, \"to\": 10184, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 11th\", \"from\": 10140, \"to\": 10148}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 10152, \"to\": 10158}, {\"ngram\": \"your side\", \"from\": 10174, \"to\": 10183}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Your defeats will be our defeats.\", \"from\": 10186, \"to\": 10220, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your defeats\", \"from\": 10187, \"to\": 10199}, {\"ngram\": \"our defeats\", \"from\": 10208, \"to\": 10219}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your victories will be our victories.\", \"from\": 10221, \"to\": 10258, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your victories\", \"from\": 10221, \"to\": 10235}, {\"ngram\": \"our victories\", \"from\": 10244, \"to\": 10257}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your emotions will be our emotions.\\\"\", \"from\": 10259, \"to\": 10295, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your emotions\", \"from\": 10259, \"to\": 10272}, {\"ngram\": \"our emotions\", \"from\": 10281, \"to\": 10293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The United Nations High Commissioner for Refugees, Filippo Grandi, has been given the Olympic Laurel.\", \"from\": 10297, \"to\": 10398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10303, \"end\": 10317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedi