0597, \"to\": 10613}, {\"ngram\": \"a real horse\", \"from\": 10635, \"to\": 10647}, {\"ngram\": \"our still-masked individual\", \"from\": 10671, \"to\": 10698}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 10732, \"to\": 10737}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 10741, \"to\": 10757}, {\"ngram\": \"a parade\", \"from\": 10762, \"to\": 10770}, {\"ngram\": \"the participating countries' flags\", \"from\": 10774, \"to\": 10808}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Quite the sight.\", \"from\": 10811, \"to\": 10827, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Quite the sight\", \"from\": 10811, \"to\": 10826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And would you believe it, the rain has stopped!\", \"from\": 10829, \"to\": 10876, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rain\", \"from\": 10855, \"to\": 10863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They have dismounted and are carrying the Olympic flag, folded in their arms towards the waiting dignitaries.\", \"from\": 10878, \"to\": 10987, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic flag\", \"from\": 10916, \"to\": 10932}, {\"ngram\": \"their arms\", \"from\": 10944, \"to\": 10954}, {\"ngram\": \"the waiting dignitaries\", \"from\": 10963, \"to\": 10986}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The flag has been delivered, and will be raised again as the Olympic anthem begins to play.\", \"from\": 10989, \"to\": 11080, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The flag\", \"from\": 10989, \"to\": 10997}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic anthem\", \"from\": 11046, \"to\": 11064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Getting word from Kevin Garside, our chief sports correspondent who's out in Paris, that our horseback rider was Floriane Issert, a warrant officer in the Gendarmerie.\", \"from\": 11082, \"to\": 11249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11161, \"end\": 11166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.794026023152485e-32, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"h